  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/bfd6d3cdebac0ac70be90b6d18955f6b.avif?t=1733785939\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras_big/bfd6d3cdebac0ac70be90b6d18955f6b.avif?t=1733785939 width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A short, creepy, immersive and primordial experience</strong> that will bring you underground, in a completely unknown place, full of <strong>puzzles</strong> to solve, hunted by a ruthless being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll find a lot of <strong>metaphoric elements</strong>, meaningful details and different, philosophical and psichological <strong>interpretations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixeled</strong> assets and minimal graphics were used here, precise and curated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is simple, filled with references from <strong>movies</strong> (Pulp Fiction, Angel Heart, more), <strong>music</strong> (Dream Theater, Ne Obliviscaris, more) and <strong>oriental cultures</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is based on original, interesting, complex <strong>puzzles</strong>, if you can't solve them, there's a walkthrough online I recorded for you, so that you can go on without getting bored!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I worked hard and really put my soul in this, so...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/7b7e80400137beec674ce4966afb4766.avif?t=1733785939\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras_big/7b7e80400137beec674ce4966afb4766.avif?t=1733785939 width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/bfd6d3cdebac0ac70be90b6d18955f6b.avif?t=1733785939\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras_big/bfd6d3cdebac0ac70be90b6d18955f6b.avif?t=1733785939 width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A short, creepy, immersive and primordial experience</strong> that will bring you underground, in a completely unknown place, full of <strong>puzzles</strong> to solve, hunted by a ruthless being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll find a lot of <strong>metaphoric elements</strong>, meaningful details and different, philosophical and psichological <strong>interpretations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixeled</strong> assets and minimal graphics were used here, precise and curated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is simple, filled with references from <strong>movies</strong> (Pulp Fiction, Angel Heart, more), <strong>music</strong> (Dream Theater, Ne Obliviscaris, more) and <strong>oriental cultures</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is based on original, interesting, complex <strong>puzzles</strong>, if you can't solve them, there's a walkthrough online I recorded for you, so that you can go on without getting bored!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I worked hard and really put my soul in this, so...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/7b7e80400137beec674ce4966afb4766.avif?t=1733785939\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras_big/7b7e80400137beec674ce4966afb4766.avif?t=1733785939 width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
